  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My memory is a little holey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's caused by a fact, which I mention in a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can remember under the age of six only a certain kind of vignettes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to take you down the street, if I would walk up from our house about four blocks, there was a square called the Square of Peace.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was going to the grammar school there in the Square of Peace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother was an extremely nice human being, a little pushy Jewish mother, who simply decided that I am born in such a year that I would have to wait for the school another year.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I went to school when I was five, which didn't bother me so much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obecna Skola na Mirovem Namesti.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I will spell it, I got myself into it-- O-B-E-C-N-A, with a line on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next one is S-- with a hooklet-- K-O-L-A, na, N-A, capital M, M-I-R-O-V-E-M Namesti, N-A-M-E-- there's an E with a hooklet S-T-I.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will avoid next time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's still called very similarly now, in spite of all the change of regimes and return to the democracy again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now, from the grade four, one could do a test into something, which would be called a high school here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We called it the gymnasium, gymnasium, which didn't mean anything when you do I mean your exercises and you train sport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was a similar type of school, which the French call a lycee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was an eight-years proposition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one could pass a special test from grade four instead of grade five.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if you passed the test, you were permitted to go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So naturally, who didn't pass the test?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
